# ğŸ“± Easy Routine

> Mobile app focused on fast routines, low cognitive load, and clear transitions between day periods.

---

## ğŸ§  Overview
**Easy Routine** is a mobile application focused on organizing daily routines in a simple, fast, and intuitive way. 

The project was designed for users who want to maintain consistency without dealing with excessive settings or complex decisions.

## ğŸ¯ Product Goals
* Fast and intuitive navigation
* Low cognitive load
* Visual clarity and consistency
* High usability on mobile screens
* Friction reduction in daily use

## ğŸ› ï¸ Scope Developed
* Mid-fidelity wireframes
* Refined visual design
* Interactive prototype in Figma
* Full componentization
* Interactive states and micro-interactions

